        {
          "type": "print_message",
          "message": "You are certain that Chil is the murderer now. After May runs from the guard, he lets May go into his house to hide, then he asks May to pretend to be crazy in the rooftop to frame Dr. Seegy that she is poisoned by him.\n\nHe may also instruct May to be wilder to attract attention with a rope that guarantees her safety. Unknowingly to May, he has already set up a mirror that is taken from 'me' to burn the rope. \n\nAt first, he wants to destroy the mirror with some mechanisms before the mechanism self-destructs, but it was gone. That's why he needs to ensure that the mirror is really gone before others realize it. Hence, he lies about his allergy.\n\nTalk to 'Pint' for the next actions."
        },
        {
          "type": "set_dialogue_stage",
          "npc": "'Pint'",
          "stage": 4
